text: Maulana Rehmatullah Khalil was a Pakistani politician who served as members of the 12th National Assembly of Pakistan from 16 November 2002 -02-10-2007. ==References== Category:Pakistani Islamic religious leaders Category:Pakistani Sunni Muslims Category:Pakistani MNAs 2002–2007 Category:Jamiat Ulema-e-Islam politicians Category:People from Peshawar
